{"tid":1369736,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] 社福界同工致香港人信 （不斷更新，陸續有黎）","createTime":"2019-07-26T18:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T13:31:00.000Z","uid":111576,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2a07001b584434c8bcccf371ce479a99616fb244","tid":1369736,"uid":111576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:45:01.000Z","msg":"[遍地開花]  社福界同工致香港人信（不斷更新，陸續有黎）<br />\nsorry 我地遲到但其實一直都係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n致香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群來自不同社福機構的同工，各自為社會上不同階層的有需要人士提供服務。縱然服務對象和工作內容各有不同，但社福界一直致力維護社會公義，為社會上弱勢、受欺壓的群眾服務，為不公義的事情發聲。<br />\n<br />\n自六月以來，在大大小小的遊行上，警方均以不恰當的武力驅散群眾，不止對示威群眾造成傷害，更影響當區居民及商鋪。於七月二十一日，在上環有警員於天橋上在未有發出警示下向群眾開槍、在元朗有黑社會於西鐵站及車廂內圍毆途人，然而令市民面對警署落閘、警員到達現場視以不見離開，甚至是999求助熱線未能接通或被掛斷等情況。這些情況都是香港市民不能接受的，社福界亦對於警隊於是次社會事件之執法及失職表示十分失望。<br />\n<br />\n就此，我們要求政府馬上成立獨立調查委員會，就警方嚴重失職的事件，以及這個多月以來的濫用暴力行為盡快展開調查。與此同時，我們亦強烈要求警方正視上述失職行為，並以專業、克制及持平的態度，去處理接下來的公眾遊行活動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我們堅持五大訴求：撤回暴動定性、撤回逃犯條例、追究警方濫暴、停止搜捕控罪、實行雙真普選。</span><br />\n社福界將一直與群眾同行。<br />\n<br />\n一群致力維護社會公義的社福界同工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FeMJRX2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFeMJRX2.jpg&h=d6b177bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFOL5h3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFOL5h3.jpg&h=90243a68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wrub0Ro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrub0Ro.jpg&h=441d9c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SuZn7wp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuZn7wp.jpg&h=cf5c3c97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u4XduKL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu4XduKL.jpg&h=145d23a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aidwgpL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaidwgpL.jpg&h=8ced1148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22bt24M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22bt24M.jpg&h=5ff2aba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HbawX6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HbawX6.jpg&h=ae090b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S6n1DC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS6n1DC7.jpg&h=7e8981da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFb: 社工罷工反送中 （整合）"},{"pid":"993c057e39fbc5f6d66923dba15eb09999c6f4b4","tid":1369736,"uid":156130,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:14:30.000Z","msg":"支持支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n社工永遠站在雞蛋一方"},{"pid":"abdbfc5a6aae86d0ad24bf5189728999a0a7a9fe","tid":1369736,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078e44a7ee20f0068f6e62252777561dd8c057ac","tid":1369736,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T21:32:18.000Z","msg":"知㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72fe66e67674417627b927591b285c8d38bd8fb","tid":1369736,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T21:33:47.000Z","msg":"wtf點解會p咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f137f5ef0c7921a6b3d55deec65303e6763ceca","tid":1369736,"uid":286781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T21:34:24.000Z","msg":"【投拆Hi】一人一信繼續投訴999，on L 9<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368627\" data-au